title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 10 - Entebbe landing challenge
description:
In this video we will look at the spotlight event which is included om Sim Update 10 beta and very likely also the final release of Sim Update 10. The landing challenge will be performed using a CJ4 and we need to use ILS to make the landing on Entebbe International Airport.
